# Weather API Keys for Real Weather Data
# Copy this file to .env and add your real API keys

# OpenWeatherMap API Key (Free tier available)
# Get your key at: https://openweathermap.org/api
VITE_OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweathermap_api_key_here

# WeatherAPI Key (Free tier available)
# Get your key at: https://www.weatherapi.com/
VITE_WEATHERAPI_KEY=your_weatherapi_key_here

# Air Quality API Key (Free tier available)
# Get your key at: https://aqicn.org/data-platform/token/
VITE_AQI_API_KEY=your_aqi_api_key_here

# UV Index API Key (Free tier available)
# Get your key at: https://www.openuv.io/
VITE_UV_API_KEY=your_uv_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Get free API keys from the providers above
# 2. Copy this file to .env (don't commit .env to git)
# 3. Replace the placeholder values with your real API keys
# 4. Restart your development server
# 5. The app will use real weather data instead of mock data

# Note: The app will still work without API keys using Open-Meteo (free, no key required)
# But for more accurate and detailed data, add your real API keys above
